summary: A feisty female nord preset for Racemenu
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][center][size=4]Hello. This is my second mod. Hopefully it works, and you enjoy it :)[/size]



[size=3]Ares is a feisty, brutal, beautiful and blood-thirsty force of nature that not many dare to reckon with. In essence, a goddess of war- hence her name. Cold, unforgiving, and  a bit arrogant at times, this dragonborn has dealt with demons- both figurative and literal- and has lived to tell the tale.[/size]
...
[size=3]...
...Yeah, I'm projecting. I love the stories, okay? you can play her any way you want, for it is just a preset. LOL

[/size]

[size=4][i][u][b]Ares is made to work on a nord female and while she may work on other races, I give no guarantees.

[/b][/u][/i][/size]
[size=5]REQUIRED MODS:[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos - Renewal[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49963/?]True Eyes[/url]

[b][size=5]RECOMMENDED MODS[/size][/b][size=3] [to make character exactly like in the screenshots]:[/size]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30936/?]Realvision ENB[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70834/?]Demoniac Texture[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37900/?]UNP BLESSED BODY- UNPB REDUX PROJECT[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72825/?]Maevan2's eye brows

[/url][b]
[size=4]CREDITS:[/size][/b]

[/center]
